(1441, 'en', 'default', '8f6225bd7662575ef84d375fec88dbd4', '<strong>Parent</strong> &mdash; You can arrange your pages in hierarchies. For example, you could have an &#8220;About&#8221; page that has &#8220;Life Story&#8221; and &#8220;My Dog&#8221; pages under it. There are no limits to how many levels you can nest pages.', NULL, 'LINE', NULL, 0, '', 'a7d363674bc0d711d6d160e3dbf13846'),
(1442, 'en', 'default', '597ef2b39aedb4e7f14e838eed92b8f7', '<strong>Template</strong> &mdash; Some themes have custom templates you can use for certain pages that might have additional features or custom layouts. If so, you&#8217;ll see them in this dropdown menu.', NULL, 'LINE', NULL, 0, '', '62319763264b08b9688c6a9f025316ba'),
(1443, 'en', 'default', 'dac04065919539b3bb81eb4152251ca4', '<strong>Order</strong> &mdash; Pages are usually ordered alphabetically, but you can choose your own order by entering a number (1 for first, etc.) in this field.', NULL, 'LINE', NULL, 0, '', 'f11c47af7f98788ea05b855c41902aa2'),
