(1944, 'en', 'default', '0f0103e212d05b86db90dd1049f37e40', 'Categories, unlike tags, can have a hierarchy. You might have a Jazz category, and under that have children categories for Bebop and Big Band. Totally optional.', NULL, 'LINE', NULL, 0, '', 'eca83cec51d51a36d40d677c793520b2'),
