ttp://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3391:\"<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-995848\" src=\"https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Compatible-Plugins-Header-300x90.png\" alt=\"Compatible Plugins-Header\" width=\"400\" height=\"121\" srcset=\"https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Compatible-Plugins-Header-300x90.png 300w, https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Compatible-Plugins-Header-150x45.png 150w, https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Compatible-Plugins-Header.png 680w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></p>\n<p>Today we are happy to announce a few WPML compatible plugins.</p>\n<p>The plugins are: <a href=\"https://shop.webtechstreet.com/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Anywhere Elementor Pro</a>, <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/indiebooking/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Indiebooking</a></p>\n<p>If you want to review the entire multilingual ready list of themes and plugins you are welcome to view it here:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/\">Multilingual Ready Themes</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/plugins-compatibility/\">Multilingual Ready Plugins</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Also, if you’re a theme or a plugin author and you want to make it compatible with WPML, we welcome you and ready to help: You are welcome to contact us at <a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/go-global-program/\">go global program page</a>.</p>\n<p>In order to expedite the process, we strongly recommend that you test your theme or plugin with our <a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/support/achieving-wpml-compatibility-for-your-themes-and-plugins/\">Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins</a>. It easily tests compatibility with WPML and helps you quickly make your theme or plugin Multilingual Ready.</p>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Anywhere Elementor Pro</h2>\n<blockquote><p>It is an addon plugin for Elementor Page Builder, which allows you to create global layouts for Single Post, Archive (like Category, Tags, Custom taxonomy, Author), Search Page and 404 Pages. </p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://shop.webtechstreet.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Purchase Anywhere Elementor Pro</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Indiebooking</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Indiebooking offers a simple and fast possibility for self-marketing of real properties / real estate.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/indiebooking/\" target=\"_blank>Download Indiebooking</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=gLCvI1pwz_0:Dnf48tbcBtc:D7DqB2pKExk\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=gLCvI1pwz_0:Dnf48tbcBtc:D7DqB2pKExk\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=gLCvI1pwz_0:Dnf48tbcBtc:gIN9vFwOqvQ\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=gLCvI1pwz_0:Dnf48tbcBtc:gIN9vFwOqvQ\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=gLCvI1pwz_0:Dnf48tbcBtc:V_sGLiPBpWU\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=gLCvI1pwz_0:Dnf48tbcBtc:V_sGLiPBpWU\" border=\"0\"></img></a>\n</div><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/wpml/~4/gLCvI1pwz_0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:64:\"https://wpml.org/2018/06/compatible-wpml-plugins-june-2018/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:59:\"https://wpml.org/2018/06/compatible-wpml-plugins-june-2018/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:6:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"WPML welcomes MultiTrans ® TMS WordPress connector\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/wpml/~3/8ZClHTmADYw/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:82:\"https://wpml.org/2018/05/wpml-welcomes-multitrans-tms-wordpress-connector/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 29 May 2018 16:59:26 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Announcements\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27:\"https://wpml.org/?p=2246896\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:400:\"We are happy to announce the recent integration of WPML and MultiTrans, a powerful translation management system. Translation Management Systems (TMS) are used to control complex translations processes in which team members (project managers, translators, editors, proofreaders) chip in their expertise.  MultiTrans Managed is a mix of software and services. It bundles linguistic teams of [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Ornela Flores\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3265:\"<h4><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-2247322\" src=\"https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/wpmlmultitrans-300x167.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"269\" height=\"150\" srcset=\"https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/wpmlmultitrans-300x167.png 300w, https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/wpmlmultitrans-150x83.png 150w, https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/wpmlmultitrans.png 360w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 269px) 100vw, 269px\" /></h4>\n<p>We are happy to announce the recent integration of <a href=\"https://wpml.org\">WPML</a> and <a href=\"https://www.donnelleylanguagesolutions.com/technology/multitrans-translation-management-system/\">MultiTrans</a>, a powerful translation management system.</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Translation Management Systems (TMS) are used to control complex translations processes in which team members (project managers, translators, editors, proofreaders) chip in their expertise. </span></p>\n<p>MultiTrans Managed is a mix of software and services. It bundles linguistic teams of project managers, translators, and editors in any workflow and connects the power of its service with a market software that reduces turn-around times and optimizes translation processes.</p>\n<p>MultiTrans serves large companies that operate in different verticals. Its services are prominent in sectors such as finance, law, life sciences, and more.</p>\n<p>With approximately 30 offices around the world, MultiTrans’ support team is able to cover all time zones and deliver any service to its global clients.</p>\n<p>Jordi Mon Companys, Global Product Marketing Manager at Donnelley Language Solutions, recommends MultiTrans to WPML users:</p>\n<blockquote><p><em>“If you are looking for a trusted partner to which you can deliver your most confidential content assets, MultiTrans from Donnelley Language Solutions is your choice. We excel at complex workflows by automating all manual tasks, coordinating the best linguistic teams in a single solution: MultiTrans Managed<img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/2.4/72x72/2122.png\" alt=\"™\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" />.”</em></p></blockquote>\n<p>If you are already a user of WPML and are interested in translating with MultiTrans, follow the instructions for<a href=\"https://wpml.org/translation-service/multitrans/\"> translating WordPress sites with MultiTrans</a>. On the other hand, if you are new to WPML, feel free to purchase the<a href=\"https://wpml.org/purchase/\"> Multilingual CMS</a> package and get started.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=8ZClHTmADYw:r-292j2UBVQ:D7DqB2pKExk\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=8ZClHTmADYw:r-292j2UBVQ:D7DqB2pKExk\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=8ZClHTmADYw:r-292j2UBVQ:gIN9vFwOqvQ\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=8ZClHTmADYw:r-292j2UBVQ:gIN9vFwOqvQ\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=8ZClHTmADYw:r-292j2UBVQ:V_sGLiPBpWU\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=8ZClHTmADYw:r-292j2UBVQ:V_sGLiPBpWU\" border=\"0\"></img></a>\n</div><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/wpml/~4/8ZClHTmADYw\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:79:\"https://wpml.org/2018/05/wpml-welcomes-multitrans-tms-wordpress-connector/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:74:\"https://wpml.org/2018/05/wpml-welcomes-multitrans-tms-wordpress-connector/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:45:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:6:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:35:\"WPML Compatible Themes – May 2018\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/wpml/~3/ugAvwudI8pg/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:67:\"https://wpml.org/2018/05/wpml-compatible-themes-may-2018-2/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"dat