\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:401:\"Today we are happy to announce a few WPML compatible WooCommerce extensions. The WooCommerce extensions are: WooCommerce Canada Post Shipping Plugin with Print Label, WooCommerce FedEx shipping plugin with Print Label, WooCommerce UPS shipping plugin with Print Label, WooCommerce Estimated Delivery Date, WooCommerce Shipping Tracking Pro If you want to review the entire multilingual ready [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Mohamed Khafaja\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5977:\"<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1119587\" src=\"https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Compatible-woocommerce-extention-header-image.png\" alt=\"compatible-woocommerce-extention-header-image\" width=\"400\" height=\"112\" srcset=\"https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Compatible-woocommerce-extention-header-image.png 568w, https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Compatible-woocommerce-extention-header-image-150x42.png 150w, https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Compatible-woocommerce-extention-header-image-300x84.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /><br />\nToday we are happy to announce a few WPML compatible WooCommerce extensions.</p>\n<p>The WooCommerce extensions are: <a href=\"https://www.xadapter.com/product/woocommerce-canada-post-shipping-plugin-with-print-label/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">WooCommerce Canada Post Shipping Plugin with Print Label</a>, <a href=\"https://www.xadapter.com/product/woocommerce-fedex-shipping-plugin-with-print-label/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">WooCommerce FedEx shipping plugin with Print Label</a>, <a href=\"https://www.xadapter.com/product/woocommerce-ups-shipping-plugin-with-print-label/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">WooCommerce UPS shipping plugin with Print Label</a>, <a href=\"https://www.xadapter.com/product/estimated-delivery-date-plugin-woocommerce/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">WooCommerce Estimated Delivery Date</a>, <a href=\"https://www.xadapter.com/product/woocommerce-shipment-tracking-pro/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">WooCommerce Shipping Tracking Pro</a></p>\n<p>If you want to review the entire multilingual ready list of themes and plugins you are welcome to view it here:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/\">Multilingual Ready Themes</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/plugins-compatibility/\">Multilingual Ready Plugins</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Also, if you’re a theme or a plugin author and you want to make it compatible with WPML, we welcome you and are ready to help: You are welcome to contact us at <a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/go-global-program/\">go global program page</a>.</p>\n<p>In order to expedite the process, we strongly recommend that you test your theme or plugin with our <a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/support/achieving-wpml-compatibility-for-your-themes-and-plugins/\">Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins</a>. It easily tests compatibility with WPML and helps you quickly make your theme or plugin Multilingual Ready.</p>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">WooCommerce Canada Post Shipping Plugin with Print Label</h2>\n<blockquote><p>WooCommerce Canada Post Shipping Plugin with Print Label is a WooCommerce extension that helps you to automate Canada Post shipping</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://www.xadapter.com/product/woocommerce-canada-post-shipping-plugin-with-print-label/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Purchase WooCommerce Canada Post Shipping Plugin with Print Label</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">WooCommerce FedEx shipping plugin with Print Label</h2>\n<blockquote><p>WooCommerce FedEx Shipping Plugin is a WooCommerce extension that helps you to completely automate FedEx shipping</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://www.xadapter.com/product/woocommerce-fedex-shipping-plugin-with-print-label/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Purchase WooCommerce FedEx shipping plugin with Print Label</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">WooCommerce UPS shipping plugin with Print Label</h2>\n<blockquote><p>WooCommerce UPS Shipping Plugin is a WooCommerce extension that helps you to completely automate UPS shipping</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://www.xadapter.com/product/woocommerce-ups-shipping-plugin-with-print-label/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Purchase WooCommerce UPS shipping plugin with Print Label</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">WooCommerce Estimated Delivery Date</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Estimated Delivery Date Plugin for WooCommerce is a simple solution in the market for providing an estimated number of days it is going to take for the product to arrive</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://www.xadapter.com/product/estimated-delivery-date-plugin-woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Purchase WooCommerce Estimated Delivery Date</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">WooCommerce Shipping Tracking Pro</h2>\n<blockquote><p>WooCommerce Shipment Tracking Plugin helps to integrate tracking functionalities to the WooCommerce shops worldwide.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://www.xadapter.com/product/woocommerce-shipment-tracking-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Purchase WooCommerce Shipping Tracking Pro</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=WKnbs66yfr8:mEB_eBaC9h8:D7DqB2pKExk\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=WKnbs66yfr8:mEB_eBaC9h8:D7DqB2pKExk\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=WKnbs66yfr8:mEB_eBaC9h8:gIN9vFwOqvQ\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=WKnbs66yfr8:mEB_eBaC9h8:gIN9vFwOqvQ\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=WKnbs66yfr8:mEB_eBaC9h8:V_sGLiPBpWU\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=WKnbs66yfr8:mEB_eBaC9h8:V_sGLiPBpWU\" border=\"0\"></img></a>\n</div><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/wpml/~4/WKnbs66yfr8\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:75:\"https://wpml.org/2018/05/compatible-woocommerce-extensions-may-2018-2/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:70:\"https://wpml.org/2018/05/compatible-woocommerce-extensions-may-2018-2/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}s:44:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/