(1109, 248, 'co_so_san_xuat', 'Brief introduction about the company: Company Limited Honoroad VN cooking oil is located in the lower Mekong River, its management system we are formed in a closed model, from the use of raw materials, production and processing to marketing, branding, sales and distribution, closed model helps us to ultimately reduce the costs of production, transportation and management, creating greater value for consumers\r\n<strong>Business Background:</strong>\r\nNatural breeding environment\r\nGeographical environment of the Mekong River Basin unique, appropriate climate year round, abundant water, good water quality, thus forming basa farming unique in the world.Currently, pangasius aquaculture industry has become the main industry of Vietnam, the annual output has reached more than 1.3 million tons, accounting for over 90% of\r\nthe world.\r\n<img src=\"http://www.honoroad.com/VIETNAM/Images/gy_07.jpg\" />\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"blank15\"></div>\r\n<img src=\"http://www.honoroad.com/VIETNAM/Images/gy_11.jpg\" />\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"wmt2\"></div>\r\n<strong>Basa processing</strong>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\nChemical scale pangasius farming sector, promote the development of processing industries in the downstream, the catfish processing plant both through the extremely rigorous inspection and certification through the countries in Europe and America region. Currently, fillet of annual exports in Vietnam reached more than 400,000 tons, mainly for export to the EU countries, the US, Latin America and Eastern Europe.\r\n<div class=\"blank15\"></div>\r\n<div><img src=\"http://www.honoroad.com/VIETNAM/Images/gy_13.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"blank15\"></div>\r\n<div><img src=\"http://www.honoroad.com/VIETNAM/Images/gy_14.jpg\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wmt1 cpbt\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"wm_fh\">\r\n<div class=\"blank15\"><strong>About the production base Co.</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"blank15\">Seafood Processing Byproducts Honoroad The fish processing fillet processing by-products contain a lot of fish oil processing, annual output can reach more than 800,000 tons. We took advantage of these materials, using physical compression technology, do not add any chemical additives, produced the first crude fat fish with an annual output of over 30,000 tons.</div>\r\n<div><img src=\"http://www.honoroad.com/VIETNAM/Images/gy_16.jpg\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><strong>Eating Oil Company Ltd. Honoroad VN</strong>\r\nWe applied machinery and refining technology, the most advanced distribution to Vietnam, conducted refining crude fish oil thereby creating fish oil products with delicious taste and healthy, the may exceed the amount of the year more than 60,000 tons, used for cooking, or for frying food sector and other industries, ..\r\n<div><img src=\"http://www.honoroad.com/VIETNAM/Images/gy_18.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"blank15\"></div>\r\n<div><img src=\"http://www.honoroad.com/VIETNAM/Images/gy_19.jpg\" /></div>\r\n</div>'),
